\"hkgmoji\" />，好期待個故仔！"},{"pid":"b287e16b2594aed0c6a0aa5ce11d44c502bd4550","tid":1851787,"uid":228854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T19:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2739e3c85e84831d987ceb40a328fbaaa093ef2a","tid":1851787,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:10:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第五章 戲弄</span></span><br />\n下課後，Miss tang走了過來<br />\n<br />\n「我而家要記你不尊心上課同不尊重老師」<br />\n<br />\n「記咪記囉」<br />\n<br />\n「唔該你態度好啲」<br />\n<br />\n「唉，得啦得啦，咪煩住哂」<br />\n<br />\nMiss tang狠狠的瞪了我一下後便走出了課室。<br />\n<br />\n「死教畜」<br />\n<br />\n我在女神心中會有甚麽印象呢？很勇敢？壞學生？不算壞吧，只是跟老師鬥鬥嘴。<br />\n<br />\n我出了課室，身體靠著欄桿<br />\n<br />\n「你咁夠薑？」一個mk味很強的人走過來<br />\n<br />\n「有咩咁好驚？」<br />\n<br />\n「你叫冼卓明？叫我阿翔得喇」<br />\n<br />\n我沒有回答他，因為我正在思考著。這跟原本的時間不同，我提早了認識mk翔。<br />\n<br />\n是因為我改變歷史的關係嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「同學，返入課室喇」prefect對我說<br />\n<br />\n剛才呆著呆著，不知鐘聲已經響起了。<br />\n<br />\n「喂，做咩啊你？上堂呆吓呆吓咁」<br />\n<br />\n「吓？咩啊」<br />\n<br />\n還以為是女神跟我說話，我原本不想回答隔離位的，要是她不是中上樣的話我會保持沉默。<br />\n<br />\n「我問你咩事，你上堂呆吓呆吓咁」<br />\n<br />\n「關你鬼事咩，你又唔係..」<br />\n<br />\n「有心事呀？講嚟聽吓」<br />\n<br />\n「同你好熟？」<br />\n<br />\n「唔想講就算啦，唔迫你喇」<br />\n<br />\n我本想出課室，但她把我拉到身邊，在我耳仔旁輕言細語。<br />\n<br />\n「你咁神秘做咩啫」<br />\n<br />\n幸好課室裏的人大致上都走了，我沒有說甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n「我對你有興...」<br />\n<br />\n「Anthea得未啊？我哋去食車仔麵啦，呢個係你男朋友？」<br />\n<br />\n原來隔離位叫Anthea，上了四個小時也不知道她的名字。<br />\n<br />\n一個不認識的女生坐在班房外，這應該是她的朋友吧。<br />\n<br />\n「唔玩你喇」Anthea走了<br />\n<br />\n「咁多女，玩哂啦」<br />\n<br />\n「你講乜呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「唔洗扮喇，啱啱嘅嘢你知我知單眼佬都知」<br />\n<br />\n「唉唔識講」<br />\n<br />\n說罷我們就走出了課室<br />\n<br />\n「頂，真係有個單眼佬」單眼佬望著我微笑<br />\n<br />\n「都話啦，陣間食咩？」<br />\n<br />\n「沙嗲牛啦」"},{"pid":"2d628b7b11b9779fbf381db966a2ad132adb317b","tid":1851787,"uid":85097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"幫推，P牌出咗文都推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6bddcef39499a77c750cb05db100f329536d87","tid":1851787,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d628b7b11b9779fbf381db966a2ad132adb317b","tid":1851787,"uid":85097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"幫推，P牌出咗文都推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f53bbf69e144214241844d351ebb1a30ee74d3","tid":1851787,"uid":316055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:24:23.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"02e14f8f99c2dbdffa62a83eedcf65086497127d","tid":1851787,"uid":246336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c2e225248e796e5f22de35f921273f54489ab3","tid":1851787,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02e14f8f99c2dbdffa62a83eedcf65086497127d","tid":1851787,"uid":246336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9823fb438a5b9a9f8133c387b1bcedb1092bff62","tid":1851787,"uid":293122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:04:39.000Z","msg":"終於有文，P牌幫吾到你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28adf122f5ed1ea8e8685e818ec95e9ec3fd1f66","tid":1851787,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9823fb438a5b9a9f8133c387b1bcedb1092bff62","tid":1851787,"uid":293122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:04:39.000Z","msg":"終於有文，P牌幫吾到你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:30:52.000Z","msg":"唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4850e6ed8186497398cdb58ddb394b9063f7c8","tid":1851787,"uid":292151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T21:44:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">第六章 咸濕仔</span></span><br />\n「啱啱條女幾正喎，有冇諗過溝佢？」<br />\n<br />\n「冇」<br />\n<br />\n「人哋仲喺你耳仔邊講嘢喎，唔食住上？」<br />\n<br />\n「你聽到佢講乜咩？」<br />\n<br />\n「聽唔到，不過咁好嘅機會你都唔把握，有食唔食最大惡極」<br />\n<br />\n「講呢啲」<br />\n<br />\n「唔講呢啲講邊啲呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「你嘅沙嗲牛肉公仔麵，凍檸茶喺度」侍應對我們說<br />\n<br />\n「食嘢啦，嘢食到」<br />\n<br />\n與創仔談天的過程中，我發覺我開始失去在原本時間線的記憶。而剛才Anthena的一舉一動好像沒有出現過？<br />\n<br />\n回到課室，Anthena與我沒有說話，整個氣場有點尷尬，可能是她在午善時的行為影響了。<br />\n<br />\n「emm..陣間上咩堂？」我先開了口<br />\n<br />\n「...」她沒有回應我<br />\n<br />\n「hi?」我在她面前揮手<br />\n<br />\n她仍然沒有反應，看來我要用必殺絕技了。我用中指彈Anthena的額頭。<br />\n<br />\n「痛啊..」<br />\n<br />\n「終於肯講嘢喇咩？」<br />\n<br />\n她再次保持沉默，但嘴角微微上揚。<br />\n<br />\n我沒有理會她，我問了其他同學後便回到坐位等待老師來。<br />\n<br />\n上課的途中，我感覺到有人在偷看我，望一望向右邊發現Anthena望著我。<br />\n<br />\n她得知被我發現後，別過頭到另一邊。<br />\n<br />\nAnthena是暗戀我嗎？還是想多了，如果她追求我的話，我可能會接受吧，畢竟我還未試過拍拖的感覺。不過我喜歡的是張靜儀。<br />\n<br />\n「做咩偷望我」我問她<br />\n<br />\n「你唔望我你點知我望你？」<br />\n<br />\n「好串喎你」<br />\n<br />\n「姐姐緊係串啲㗎啦」<br />\n<br />\n「乜你大過我咩？」<br />\n<br />\n「係啊，我留過兩年班」<br />\n<br />\n「咁你今年要努力啲喇喎」<br />\n<br />\n「你都係啦」<br />\n<br />\n「咁我哋一齊加油啦」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯」<br />\n<br />\n我舉起了左手示意做個high five，Anthena也很配合我。<br />\n<br />\n我拍了後感覺不對勁，這種感覺軟軟的。<br />\n<br />\n她望了一望胸部後用手遮蓋著，臉紅紅地對我說。<br />\n<br />\n「揸完未啊咸濕仔」<br />\n<br />\nAnthena這句話驚動了老師，情景比如payday2裏的保安發現了玩家，然後大大個紅色的感歎號出現在頭上。<br />\n<br />\n「角落頭嗰度ok嗎？跟唔跟到？」<br />\n<br />\n「冇問題冇問題」<br />\n<br />\n「你差啲害死我喇」<br />\n<br />\n「鬼叫你一嘢拍落嚟我個胸咩」<br />\n<br />\n「sorly，sorly冇心」<br />\n<br />\n「嬲你啊，咸濕仔」<br />\n<br />\n「對唔住囉，唔好嬲啦」<br />\n<br />\n她沒有理會我<br />\n<br />\n「咁...你打返我幾下當補償返」<br />\n<br />\n左一拳右一拳然後再打多拳，如事者，我的手臂被Anthena打了三下。<br />\n<br />\n「洗唔洗咁大力啊」<br />\n<br />\n「知死未？」<br />\n<br />\n她拿了一本書，向我的頭打。<br />\n<br />\n「對唔住對唔住對唔住」<br />\n<br />\n沒想到開學的第一天就很「黑仔」"},{"pid":"2f9e166610929055a58596283f8ec2864a9f240d","tid":1851787,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:11:39.000Z","msg":"咁耐都冇出到文係因為寫寫吓變咗甜故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後係咁改嚟改去所以搞勁耐都冇文 <br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位巴絲繼續支持小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以follow返我個ig sevennot7同埋想睇得舒服啲可以去紙言睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5087be28e6365e3917c89f89104ecfc097bc13","tid":1851787,"uid":85097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"有文繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c5e8ed1c1b92c777a5ffb86d8c95fb38c0aeb2","tid":1851787,"uid":81503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:59:06.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f4635722ca10e99815ddbfd021af4b463e2db64e","tid":1851787,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:09:52.000Z","msg":"7093 被列入戰略物資<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1882208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1882208</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"03047bb854c14035bc273c6206a15bf8a7ee58fd","tid":1851787,"uid":293122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f9e166610929055a58596283f8ec2864a9f240d","tid":1851787,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:11:39.000Z","msg":"咁耐都冇出到文係因為寫寫吓變咗甜故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後係咁改嚟改去所以搞勁耐都冇文 <br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位巴絲繼續支持小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以follow返我個ig sevennot7同埋想睇得舒服啲可以去紙言睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoh